'''Colloidal fuel''' is an [[emulsion]] of powdered [[coal]] in [[kerosene]].  It was used in World War I aboard ships as kerosene supplies ran low.<ref>{{Cite book|url = https://books.google.com/books?id=KikDAAAAMBAJ|title = Popular Science|last = Corporation|first = Bonnier|date = 1919-07-01|publisher = [[Bonnier Corporation]]|language = en}}</ref>

