'''''Hardy Perennials and Old Fashioned Flowers — Describing the Most Desirable Plants, for Borders, Rockeries, and Shrubberies''''' is a [[horticulture]] and [[gardening]] book published in 1884 by [[John George Wood|John Wood]]. 

The book was also published by the [[Project Gutenberg|Project Gutenberg Literary Archive Foundation]] in 2006.

