{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Ixora'' species}}
The genus ''[[Ixora]]'' is one of the [[list of the largest genera of flowering plants|largest genera of flowering plants]] and contains around 562 species from the [[Rubiaceae]] family. Detailed, up to date information can be found on [http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/ the World Checklist of Rubiaceae].
